<node id="Paths">
  <data key="d0">Paths</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Paths refer to node sequences in flow graphs, representing different execution routes through the code.&lt;SEP&gt;Paths and their role in white-box based test design are discussed.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fb105fc5954ed7ecb73c560e551b6191&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4320b5806b340aa80c399ed230ca5ef7</data>
