  <data key="d0">Company Logo</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Company Logo should be linked to the Home-page.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b4ab47d35eeaee4c5eceb6f8589fa909</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1770830329</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="404 Page">
  <data key="d0">404 Page</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">A 404 Page or any custom designed Not Found page should be present in a website.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b4ab47d35eeaee4c5eceb6f8589fa909</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1770830330</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Alt Tags">
  <data key="d0">Alt Tags</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Appropriate ALT tags should be added for images.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b4ab47d35eeaee4c5eceb6f8589fa909</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1770830330</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Test Planner">
  <data key="d0">Test Planner</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">The Test Planner gives an overall description of the project, the software system being developed or maintained, and the software items and/or features to be tested. The Test Planner should also include items that will not be included in the test effort.&lt;SEP&gt;The test planner needs tools and techniques to estimate test costs.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6ff2808b9a579f74a66fa6fdc41222f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-31e1a59391bc5c57ad4d5941cffbeb6b</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1770830464</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Software System">
  <data key="d0">Software System</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Software System is being developed or maintained, and the Software System is tested.&lt;SEP&gt;A software system encompasses the software product and associated artifacts like plans, documents, code, and manuals.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6ff2808b9a579f74a66fa6fdc41222f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c7b18e88c7970da3d28ba996629ad181&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8139eb8fe9a7e279b24055af3d6cb375</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1770830772</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Software Testing">
  <data key="d0">Software Testing</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Software Testing is a critical process dedicated to evaluating software applications to identify defects, ensure they meet specified requirements, and function correctly. It serves as both a field of study and a practice, devoted to the verification and validation of software products. This process involves planned and systematic activities designed to detect discrepancies between given input and expected outcomes.

Software Testing encompasses various methods and techniques to evaluate the quality and reliability of software. It involves exercising a software component using a selected set of test cases to reveal defects and evaluate quality. The evaluation aims to verify and validate that the software meets specified requirements and user expectations. The ultimate goal is to establish that the software has attained a desired level of quality with respect to selected attributes and to confirm its functionality. It's a practice used to set testing goals and evaluate test data.

Furthermore, Software Testing focuses on organizational issues and perceptions related to testing, requiring repeatable experiments, planning, and integration into the software life cycle. Various aspects of testing are covered, such as unit, integration, and black box testing. Software testing services can be outsourced to external companies specializing in this area. Specific areas of focus include test infrastructure management, test people management, integrating testing with product release cycles, the challenges inherent in software testing, staffing considerations, and suitable organizational structures to support testing efforts.&lt;SEP&gt;Software testing is the process of evaluating software to find defects and ensure quality.&lt;SEP&gt;Software testing is a process to evaluate the functionality of a software application.&lt;SEP&gt;Software testing is implied as the overall topic of the text.&lt;SEP&gt;Software testing is the overarching activity the text discusses, aimed at identifying and improving software quality.&lt;SEP&gt;Software Testing is the subject of the document.&lt;SEP&gt;Software Testing is a set of planned activities to check if software behavior matches expectations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6ff2808b9a579f74a66fa6fdc41222f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5dc410bc2f23656e00ef58bd19840cb4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-56db660e3609aef43610e61aa17e8a81&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-30509fdeb65cdfc4b7aaea9954573044&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c7cd0ee78ddf28561be524a34f8204f8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4320b5806b340aa80c399ed230ca5ef7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-194ddef519cf128899a2be4c3247d7cc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d305f3df506b1970c8b64e4f97aec802&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-576c3b5853abc31c233b7f55290db336&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fd156cdc428160086f8586613843cba1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1d2b4e5470a5fae4ac0a621246515793&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-38fe44206894ac154ea53b46f05d2387&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c06066fef21175272ed95dcceb2a37a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c584edf6e5f2b8db471597d14e5d0bd0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1885c8cabab1027faeb9afbaf3f0ddc5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fb22ba0e1a3621e7dc6f377089c45524&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0311ba388d3d3bfed0911e54d252ae1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1f2f00224294bd5a13c502fab087870d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ef2e90aeeaaea52d08d7eed63146a5f5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3bf5c8faaf5457d884ede4bf2b9900ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c7b18e88c7970da3d28ba996629ad181&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d1d7014ef279c74a7acb5889dca6440&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4a2a0fc342861ce4f51a3e5784bf82da&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0ad834ab92932d983e93d86d224421e9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4172dd84636c7dab653ead0e84fbdaf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-413abe27441aa74b0b434e98bea575fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1f50a0acff86b61f2aebdc6201bedb80&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a9004c9fb37134adfd3b872db4e4a036&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0bc02d92c94be7170edbcd55893256aa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-50ee503f2fae49523a55b9fcdc5df8d1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4e1d6f42b98e3c56f98bec31ea6b1c40&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-30553e0ee44e2324f5640d522949d67d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bc034242c01926773d32a19ffb90ce40&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e67f594ae3047aebaed5c7bf8c5ee26&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab025a6280cae81005d1ff3a3a08029e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac6e3a12af74abf6be605f347823c7a8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dbc728752df68dcf9cf8ae1e0942cee8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-da9b3662c0429d5ef91b33c626c7ba44&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7814e3a12bbf4d4dc88df26f6fc2b9f0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8230b787a8fe42514cbd735e327e0d20&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6293aec7ed87430ba4236ef6fa4fc8a2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-777f4f5fd36fe745076f0229587eef55&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a8c81f7a1e1c30a9a414bb702063e460&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-730afa5a03e337a9a1b2ed3ad640133d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4600873a7185719f33d700ae5a5d121&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-55856660a2522d1670370f74ea265c8e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d54ee8dd0e2b5ff1654ab561620b6c44&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac3c02729685274cd9387cadef0dc333&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-994f0b8030636c42759ae6d6ee2baddc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a3d4647a1870ce91c199e09abfe6968e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dfa4585fbbedcc4f123eb8d583c669ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cfbe20c55205b7267c83b935777d953d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-588cab56860b1b61b223c01b7307a5a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-226d94c07ca09316fdcba5b872e40b9d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8e0b2f4de41f85e92858a47a98a81b2d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d460fa457eb3a013c4e2949dd7c5d083&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52bc934fcfeec89646ffbc42ac44a30a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09aff991601cb8d11a8b32035d5ed5c8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed0e4731c3296bc5ba3ae5edf4cd9631&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f9a1e0b0e37c96741aefa49dc8030cdc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-90608f1fe255e95bf5a4da4744ec4c35&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b1985b2f00f63e1c64f0933bd04e3e13&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dadd5fedffda581a4f86164ce8358084&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c865455d56f087310ad4a2872dcee595&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c7f1235e8106bb7153b375709adaf33&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-69c0cfe4a2b7b48410d36c1025bd36b7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1770831870</data>
