<node id="Test Plans">
  <data key="d0">Test Plans</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Test Plans are developed as multilevel documents.&lt;SEP&gt;Test plans are items selected for review to validate the testing approach and coverage for multiple levels.&lt;SEP&gt;Test plans for software projects are complex and detailed documents that include overall test objectives and risks.&lt;SEP&gt;Test plans are documents developed for each level of testing, specifying objectives and ensuring adequate time and resources are allocated.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6ff2808b9a579f74a66fa6fdc41222f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-71fc4f34702301e4dd6c1ae7beda783b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-51f22a0f26d6d401d4a1e4f700c30a8e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab025a6280cae81005d1ff3a3a08029e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1770831099</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
