<node id="Classes">
  <data key="d0">Classes</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Classes are an example of an item that could be listed as something to be tested.&lt;SEP&gt;Classes are blueprints for creating objects, encapsulating data and methods.&lt;SEP&gt;Classes are a concept in object-oriented programming.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6ff2808b9a579f74a66fa6fdc41222f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0682a23253488e1a8adf8e634de7e049&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4600873a7185719f33d700ae5a5d121</data>
