<node id="User Manual">
  <data key="d0">User Manual</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The User Manual is a document that should be referenced.&lt;SEP&gt;The User Manual serves as a source for developing black box tests at the integration level.&lt;SEP&gt;The User Manual is relevant to Integration Test Planning and contains information for planning the integration test.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6ff2808b9a579f74a66fa6fdc41222f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8230b787a8fe42514cbd735e327e0d20&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-55856660a2522d1670370f74ea265c8e</data>
