<node id="Status Report">
  <data key="d0">Status Report</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">A status report, or summary report, is signed by all participants in inspections.&lt;SEP&gt;Status Reports are published by the project manager and test managers to inform management of project and test progress.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1a701e33391919caf4151b2a9d6fa069&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c7f1235e8106bb7153b375709adaf33</data>
