  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1770830378</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Developer">
  <data key="d0">Developer</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">The Developer is a stakeholder that the testing strategy should be flexible to.&lt;SEP&gt;The developer uses the test log for defect repair.&lt;SEP&gt;A developer performs static testing and builds debug versions of the product to check for mistakes and complex logic.&lt;SEP&gt;A developer is someone who creates and develops software.&lt;SEP&gt;The Developer is responsible for using past experience and intuition to design test cases for Error Guessing.&lt;SEP&gt;The developer is the individual who writes the code and prepares it for unit testing.&lt;SEP&gt;An individual responsible for the item.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c7cd0ee78ddf28561be524a34f8204f8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-576c3b5853abc31c233b7f55290db336&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c584edf6e5f2b8db471597d14e5d0bd0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1f2f00224294bd5a13c502fab087870d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ff3bcd5d811cf1d3238112df22f24549&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1f50a0acff86b61f2aebdc6201bedb80&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac3c02729685274cd9387cadef0dc333</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1770831428</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
