</node>
<node id="Defects">
  <data key="d0">Defects</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Defects are found out during software testing.&lt;SEP&gt;Defects are bugs or issues found during software testing that highlight loopholes in the testing process.&lt;SEP&gt;Defects are errors or flaws in software that cause it to produce incorrect or unexpected results.&lt;SEP&gt;Defects are flaws or errors found during software testing.&lt;SEP&gt;Defects are a main factor taken into account for reliability testing.&lt;SEP&gt;Defects refer to the problems found in the software during testing, which can cause failures.&lt;SEP&gt;Defects are identified through customer feedback during beta testing and are prioritized for fixing.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c7cd0ee78ddf28561be524a34f8204f8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9ea23d51412441d95fd9957313b3d478&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0ad834ab92932d983e93d86d224421e9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1f50a0acff86b61f2aebdc6201bedb80&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dac674a5a618326bac489f8124a35c69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cfbe20c55205b7267c83b935777d953d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-588cab56860b1b61b223c01b7307a5a5</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1770831561</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Requirements Documents">
  <data key="d0">Requirements Documents</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Requirements documents are items selected for review to ensure that the project meets its intended objectives.&lt;SEP&gt;Requirements Documents serve as a source for developing black box tests at the integration level.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-71fc4f34702301e4dd6c1ae7beda783b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8230b787a8fe42514cbd735e327e0d20</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1770831175</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Design Documents">
  <data key="d0">Design Documents</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Design documents are items selected for review to verify that the design aligns with the requirements and project goals.&lt;SEP&gt;Design Documents describe the target units and provide inputs for the unit test plan.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-71fc4f34702301e4dd6c1ae7beda783b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42669b4fcb6bce2882145c03df26e5f5</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1770831286</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
