  <data key="d0">Usability</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Usability is evaluated during software testing.&lt;SEP&gt;Usability relates to the degree of effort needed to learn, operate, prepare input, and interpret output of the software.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c7cd0ee78ddf28561be524a34f8204f8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0c000d3c006e3afe689c5531f61cede1</data>
