  <data key="d0">User Manuals</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">User manuals are items selected for review to confirm they accurately guide users on how to use the software.&lt;SEP&gt;User manuals are documents that provide instructions on how to use the software.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-71fc4f34702301e4dd6c1ae7beda783b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fcbf2b63fbccb6dd9180c41126c64053</data>
