<node id="Functionality">
  <data key="d0">Functionality</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Understanding the Functionality is a goal of a smart tester.&lt;SEP&gt;Functionality relates to the existence of properties and functions that satisfy user needs.&lt;SEP&gt;Functionality is a key aspect to be tested and ensured during integration testing, alongside performance and other requirements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c7cd0ee78ddf28561be524a34f8204f8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c2d7d142472e7acf420224383c99b13b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8230b787a8fe42514cbd735e327e0d20</data>
