<node id="SQA Staff">
  <data key="d0">SQA Staff</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">SQA staff are members of the review team.&lt;SEP&gt;SQA staff are members of the configuration control board.&lt;SEP&gt;SQA staff are part of the team to evaluate the effectiveness of the testing efforts using the Test Summary Report.&lt;SEP&gt;The SQA Staff attends milestone meetings.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-71fc4f34702301e4dd6c1ae7beda783b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8139eb8fe9a7e279b24055af3d6cb375&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2b3c34fc8c737800e72c4ba3dd2c8eff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c7f1235e8106bb7153b375709adaf33</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1770831864</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Testers">
  <data key="d0">Testers</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Testers are members of the review team.&lt;SEP&gt;Testers are involved in estimating testing costs along with the project manager and developers.&lt;SEP&gt;Testers run the tests and record results.&lt;SEP&gt;Testers work with project managers and the Software Quality Assurance Group to develop quality-related policies and quality assurance plans.&lt;SEP&gt;Testers are individuals who need comprehensive knowledge of software engineering, fault types, and the problem domain.&lt;SEP&gt;Testers are responsible for designing test cases to ensure all modules are called and for working with requirements analysts to ensure requirements are testable, accurate, and complete.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-71fc4f34702301e4dd6c1ae7beda783b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c7cd0ee78ddf28561be524a34f8204f8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-31e1a59391bc5c57ad4d5941cffbeb6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-08aa6af3aad54d106fc55a5710f36151&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d1d7014ef279c74a7acb5889dca6440&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab025a6280cae81005d1ff3a3a08029e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8230b787a8fe42514cbd735e327e0d20</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1770831181</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Environment">
  <data key="d0">Environment</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Understanding the Environment is a goal of a smart tester.</data>
