</node>
<node id="Management">
  <data key="d0">Management</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Management is a source of potential problems for testers if testing is not planned correctly.&lt;SEP&gt;Management refers to a fee structure category based on management quota.&lt;SEP&gt;Management is responsible for resource allocation and sending messages, influencing perceptions of testing.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c7cd0ee78ddf28561be524a34f8204f8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52bc4ae0ed75d4c9e063e984a954b88b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4172dd84636c7dab653ead0e84fbdaf</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1770830854</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Developers">
  <data key="d0">Developers</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Developers play multifaceted roles throughout the software development lifecycle. They are fundamentally responsible for developing software.

Beyond coding, developers actively participate in various teams and processes. They are members of the review team and the configuration control board. They collaborate with the project manager and testers to estimate testing costs. During testing phases, developers receive test information crucial for debugging and duplicating test conditions. They are also involved in Alpha Testing, typically conducted at the developing organization's location.

Furthermore, developers contribute to evaluating the effectiveness of testing efforts, utilizing the Test Summary Report. While developers excel at creating code, they may face challenges in effectively testing their own code, highlighting the importance of diverse testing perspectives.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-71fc4f34702301e4dd6c1ae7beda783b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-31e1a59391bc5c57ad4d5941cffbeb6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-38fe44206894ac154ea53b46f05d2387&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8139eb8fe9a7e279b24055af3d6cb375&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab025a6280cae81005d1ff3a3a08029e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2b3c34fc8c737800e72c4ba3dd2c8eff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72174c906a600ada847dff60ecc94505&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09aff991601cb8d11a8b32035d5ed5c8</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1770831757</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
