  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Special environmental needs include specific hardware and hardware configurations needed to execute the test case, as well as software like compilers, simulators, and test coverage tools.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-194ddef519cf128899a2be4c3247d7cc</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1770830444</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
