</node>
<node id="Purpose">
  <data key="d0">Purpose</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The purpose describes the goal of the test procedure and references any test cases it executes.&lt;SEP&gt;Purpose is a component of a test case semantic network, describing the goal of the test case.</data>
