  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">A compiler is a software tool that translates source code into machine code.&lt;SEP&gt;A compiler is a program that translates source code into machine code.&lt;SEP&gt;Compiler is a software used to generate product binaries.&lt;SEP&gt;A compiler is an example of a language processor.</data>
