<node id="Functional Testing">
  <data key="d0">Functional Testing</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Functional testing involves product features and functionality to test product behavior.&lt;SEP&gt;Functional Testing is a type of testing that Usability Testing can support.&lt;SEP&gt;Functional testing evaluates whether the software meets specified requirements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-57b5bdf87e3c8352e48d198a65913eb1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2ae86184847a25f93edb5f375e4378fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4600873a7185719f33d700ae5a5d121</data>
