  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Integration is a testing phase.&lt;SEP&gt;Integration is defined as the set of interactions among components.&lt;SEP&gt;Integration is a level of software testing.&lt;SEP&gt;Integration is a method that defines interfaces for two or more components within a product.</data>
