  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Service level agreements is an acceptance criteria.&lt;SEP&gt;Service level agreements define the time required for the testing team to complete testing.&lt;SEP&gt;Service level agreements are the commitments made by the software provider regarding the level of service that will be provided.</data>
