<node id="Near-Site Team">
  <data key="d0">Near-Site Team</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The near-site team is a small team placed at or near the customer location.&lt;SEP&gt;The Near-Site Team is mentioned in relation to the Remote Team, potentially having a peer-to-peer relationship or reporting to the Remote Team Manager.</data>
