  <data key="d0">Structural Testing</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Structural testing involves testing the code structure and internal design by running tests on the built product.&lt;SEP&gt;Structural testing is testing the structure.&lt;SEP&gt;Structural testing examines the internal structure and code of a program.</data>
