<node id="Software Artifact">
  <data key="d0">Software Artifact</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">A Software Artifact is evaluated during a review, but the review should not evaluate the developer or author of the artifact.&lt;SEP&gt;A software artifact is evaluated in a review meeting.&lt;SEP&gt;A software artifact represents any tangible outcome of the software development process.&lt;SEP&gt;A Software Artifact is a component that undergoes review for potential improvements, defect detection, and standards conformance.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c2d7d142472e7acf420224383c99b13b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8139eb8fe9a7e279b24055af3d6cb375&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52bc934fcfeec89646ffbc42ac44a30a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c865455d56f087310ad4a2872dcee595</data>
