<node id="Test Automation">
  <data key="d0">Test Automation</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Test automation involves developing software to automatically test other software, offering advantages such as time-saving and improved reliability.&lt;SEP&gt;Test Automation is the use of automated tools and techniques to perform software testing.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fb22ba0e1a3621e7dc6f377089c45524&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-adc0f944e298fc1492f619b8a593d383</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
