  <data key="d0">Software Developer</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Software Developer is a professional involved in creating software.&lt;SEP&gt;Software developer includes software engineers, programmers, analysts, and testers.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d0311ba388d3d3bfed0911e54d252ae1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-69c0cfe4a2b7b48410d36c1025bd36b7</data>
