  <data key="d0">Software Engineering</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Software Engineering is an emerging formal engineering discipline.&lt;SEP&gt;Software engineering is the discipline concerned with the development and maintenance of software systems.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d0311ba388d3d3bfed0911e54d252ae1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c7b18e88c7970da3d28ba996629ad181</data>
