<node id="Decision Table">
  <data key="d0">Decision Table</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">A Decision Table is a method to denote a list of decision variables, conditions set for every decision variable, and actions to be done in each combination of the conditions.&lt;SEP&gt;A Decision Table has rows for each cause and effect, reflecting rules and entities in a cause and effect graph.&lt;SEP&gt;A Decision Table is converted from the graph.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-52bc4ae0ed75d4c9e063e984a954b88b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ff3bcd5d811cf1d3238112df22f24549&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dadd5fedffda581a4f86164ce8358084</data>
