<node id="Unit Test">
  <data key="d0">Unit Test</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Unit test involves designing test cases and test procedures to validate individual software units.&lt;SEP&gt;Unit test is a software testing method where individual units or components of a software are tested.&lt;SEP&gt;Unit test is a level of software testing where individual components are tested to detect functional and structural defects.&lt;SEP&gt;Unit test refers to testing individual units or components of the software.&lt;SEP&gt;A type of software testing that focuses on individual units or components of the software.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0682a23253488e1a8adf8e634de7e049&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1f50a0acff86b61f2aebdc6201bedb80&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bc034242c01926773d32a19ffb90ce40&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4600873a7185719f33d700ae5a5d121&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed0e4731c3296bc5ba3ae5edf4cd9631</data>
