  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">C2 represents one of the causes in the Decision Table.&lt;SEP&gt;C2 represents the condition that the character to search for is in the string.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ff3bcd5d811cf1d3238112df22f24549&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dadd5fedffda581a4f86164ce8358084</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
