<node id="Plan">
  <data key="d0">Plan</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A plan is a document that provides a framework or approach for achieving a set of goals, describing tasks, responsibilities, tools, time, resources, and milestones.&lt;SEP&gt;Plan is the value or level an organization plans to achieve for a quality metric to satisfy users/clients.</data>
