<node id="Software Quality Metrics Methodology">
  <data key="d0">Software Quality Metrics Methodology</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Software Quality Metrics Methodology is a five-step process for establishing quality requirements, applying software metrics, and analyzing results. It is adapted from IEEE Std 1061-1992.</data>
