  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The Requirements Document serves as a knowledge source for black box testing, outlining the expected behavior of the software.&lt;SEP&gt;The Requirements Document is relevant to Integration Test Planning and contains structure charts, state charts, and data dictionaries.</data>
