  <data key="d0">Effort Variance</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Effort Variance is a metric related to effort distribution.&lt;SEP&gt;Effort Variance is a metric that measures the difference between estimated and actual effort in software development phases.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-30553e0ee44e2324f5640d522949d67d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2e450de8294677410b0dfa671b57c74f</data>
