  <data key="d0">Schedule Variance</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Schedule Variance is a metric related to scheduling.&lt;SEP&gt;Schedule Variance is the deviation of the actual schedule from the estimated schedule.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-30553e0ee44e2324f5640d522949d67d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2e450de8294677410b0dfa671b57c74f</data>
